{"tid":2309413,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打試過搵非行貨代理車行買二手車？","createTime":"2020-12-02T13:50:50.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-02T14:02:26.000Z","uid":63371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"56b70cbfb3eeeb074dd7fa73e1f7b99d64f8d401","tid":2309413,"uid":63371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:50:50.000Z","msg":"唔係買水貨，都係指買行貨<br />\n成日話啲車行積木車，扮直板執靚仔搵水魚賣畀下手，實情係咪真係咁黑暗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？<br />\n<br />\n計0-1首車嘅話你哋會㨂私讓，完全唔考慮車行定有巴打係車行買車有好嘅經驗分享<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a42a3d1717d643dc08572e8a05883010fa8a2e9","tid":2309413,"uid":18363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:53:56.000Z","msg":"冇必要唔會揀車行<br />\n真係要係車行買車就會搵個熟車既識整車既朋友一齊睇"},{"pid":"9beedef10fb2b998c6bb7400ece2395a8ff1a296","tid":2309413,"uid":11858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62263dde6f52822fbd8fe1b619b34d659b16e545","tid":2309413,"uid":54511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T14:02:26.000Z","msg":"好早期（幾年前） 時時見fb 賣廣告 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有個驗車服務  唔記得幾錢 有個驗車師 同你一齊去睇/驗<br />\n<br />\n講解比你知 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/tea.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果你怕 整過/大整/又唔識車既又驚比人搵笨 應該幫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}